reviewText: So glad I bought this set! The DVD quality is much better. Skateboarding needs On Video Again. Wish I could find them all on DVD.

after the new dc movie came out danny way is now easily the most talented skater on the planet. he cant do mullens techest tricks, but noone can do what he does off the dc mega roller....the 'on' danny way issue shows the public what it took to become the living legend he is today...........
